<li>Bonze Age Collapse: 
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Great mystery.</li>
<li>Something/Someone destroyed many (most all) the great bronze age civilisations</li>
<li>Happened extremely suddenly, not sure what caused it.</li>
<li>Almost unparralleled in histogry (Collapse of the Roman empire comes close)</li>
<li>Utterly changed (degraded) life for the peoples of the time</li>
<li>Ushered in a dark ages (far darker/longer) than "the dark ages" (After the fall of the Roman empire)</li>
<li>Cautionary tale for us today. Great/Advanced civilisations can be easily, and quickly, obliterated.</li>
</ul></li>

<li>"Steppe People"
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Critical role throughout history.</li>
