<li>Impact of the Black Death (1340s - 1350s)

<ul class="org-ul">
<li>killed 1/2 the population had major societal impacts.</li>
<li>Killed many of the clergy and resulted in them being replaced by younger, less devoted people.</li>
<li>Lead (many think) to the reformation and the enlightenment.</li>
</ul></li>

